WEBVTT

00:06.048 --> 00:09.217
In a world of chaos,
some things never change...

00:09.218 --> 00:11.344
that good will always win...

00:11.345 --> 00:13.889
You stay the fuck back
or I'll laser you, goddamn it!

00:14.598 --> 00:16.516
...that love conquers all...

00:16.517 --> 00:18.059
I'm your father, not him.

00:18.060 --> 00:19.978
- Ryan!
-  ...and that heroes

00:19.979 --> 00:22.814
will-will answer the call to protect...

00:28.863 --> 00:30.530
I want to flip A-Train. He's right there.

00:30.531 --> 00:31.573
He's ready.

00:31.574 --> 00:33.908
When I carried your ass
to the ER, that felt better

00:33.909 --> 00:36.745
than anything
that I'd ever done at Vought.

00:36.746 --> 00:38.329
The answer to all our prayers.

00:38.330 --> 00:40.081
A virus that kills Supes.

00:40.082 --> 00:41.292
Somebody's been running tests.

00:41.959 --> 00:43.460
To make the virus

00:43.461 --> 00:44.961
strong enough to kill Homelander

00:44.962 --> 00:47.547
would evolve it
into something super lethal.

00:47.548 --> 00:49.716
A global fucking pandemic.

00:49.717 --> 00:51.468
What's a little genocide between friends?

00:51.469 --> 00:53.678
Just fuck off and let me die in peace,
would you?

00:53.679 --> 00:55.764
The Seven is getting even stronger.

00:55.765 --> 00:58.099
Put your hands together for Firecracker!

00:58.100 --> 00:59.934
I am not sexually attracted to you.

00:59.935 --> 01:01.227
It's about loyalty.

01:01.228 --> 01:03.855
I'd do anything for you.

01:03.856 --> 01:04.856
And Sister Sage!

01:04.857 --> 01:06.608
She's the world's
smartest person.

01:06.609 --> 01:07.859
Fascist!

01:07.860 --> 01:10.737
The people will tear it apart themselves.

01:10.738 --> 01:12.405
Then you get to swoop in...

01:12.406 --> 01:14.699
- Like Caesar.
- Like Caesar.

01:14.700 --> 01:16.242
Once he's in office,

01:16.243 --> 01:17.786
we need to invoke the 25th Amendment.

01:17.787 --> 01:18.745
Who's handling all this?

01:18.746 --> 01:20.580
- I fucking am.
-  When Homelander

01:20.581 --> 01:22.415
chucks all the Starlighters
into internment camps,

01:22.416 --> 01:23.666
you're cool with that?

01:23.667 --> 01:24.584
You didn't know about the camps.

01:24.585 --> 01:26.336
You're gonna help us take down Vought
and Homelander.

01:26.337 --> 01:27.755
No deals.

01:31.091 --> 01:32.258
Neuman would have been a shit patsy.

01:32.259 --> 01:33.301
So I went another way.

01:33.302 --> 01:34.511
Speaker of the House Calhoun.

01:34.512 --> 01:35.678
He's next in line to be president.

01:35.679 --> 01:36.888
He'd like to pledge his allegiance to you.

01:36.889 --> 01:39.057
Now that we have
full legal authority...

01:39.058 --> 01:41.059
- No!
- ...a veritable army of superheroes

01:41.060 --> 01:42.268
will be called upon

01:42.269 --> 01:46.022
to rout these traitors from our government
and from our streets.

01:46.023 --> 01:48.149
America will be safe again.

01:48.150 --> 01:49.859
And to the Starlighters,

01:49.860 --> 01:51.986
I'm coming for you. Because today

01:51.987 --> 01:54.489
a new age of superheroes begins.

01:54.490 --> 01:55.907
-  You were my first call.
-  You got to be

01:55.908 --> 01:58.077
fucking kidding me.
This whole time.

02:14.468 --> 02:16.595
Yeah! Whoo!

02:30.568 --> 02:34.320
USA! USA! USA!

02:34.321 --> 02:39.200
USA! USA! USA! USA!

02:39.201 --> 02:40.619
- Thank you.
- USA!

02:41.954 --> 02:43.162
Thank you!

02:43.163 --> 02:44.622
Thank you and welcome

02:44.623 --> 02:48.126
to the Vought International
Annual Meeting of Shareholders.

02:52.673 --> 02:55.049
Okay.
Give me my Firecrackers.

02:55.050 --> 02:56.634
That's places, ladies, places.

02:56.635 --> 02:58.803
Let's go, let's go.

02:58.804 --> 03:01.431
Hop to it. Let's go. Come on.

03:01.432 --> 03:03.266
Stay in line. Keep it tight.

03:03.267 --> 03:05.643
Copy. I've got them heading
to the wings now.

03:05.644 --> 03:07.270
Front row, you're on the spike marks.

03:07.271 --> 03:08.897
Second row, right behind them.

03:23.621 --> 03:25.455
Wasn't that long ago

03:25.456 --> 03:28.166
we were lost in the darkness.

03:28.167 --> 03:30.543
Starlighters running wild.

03:30.544 --> 03:33.463
Starlight herself
on a vicious murder spree.

03:33.464 --> 03:35.506
But we said no.

03:35.507 --> 03:37.008
We said, "Enough."

03:37.009 --> 03:39.761
We said, "Not in America."

03:39.762 --> 03:41.971
And together we soared

03:41.972 --> 03:44.641
into a new golden dawn!

03:57.237 --> 04:00.615
Our superheroes are now
the ranking law enforcement officers...

04:00.616 --> 04:01.617
Keep going.

04:04.370 --> 04:05.245
Stop!

04:07.456 --> 04:09.123
We designated the Starlighters

04:09.124 --> 04:11.000
a terrorist organization.

04:11.001 --> 04:14.462
Other heroes are proudly serving
in the armed forces

04:14.463 --> 04:17.590
thanks to the new chairman
of the Joint Chiefs, General Mayhem!

04:17.591 --> 04:19.425
Net income

04:19.426 --> 04:21.260
is up 21%.

04:21.261 --> 04:22.762
G-Men:

04:22.763 --> 04:25.598
Days Past from the Future has grossed over

04:25.599 --> 04:26.933
two billion.

04:26.934 --> 04:29.519
And do not get me started
on the EBITDA margins.

04:29.520 --> 04:30.895
But all of this

04:30.896 --> 04:32.855
pales in comparison to the most

04:32.856 --> 04:34.440
important truth,

04:34.441 --> 04:36.401
that this is

04:36.402 --> 04:37.694
a safer,

04:37.695 --> 04:40.863
more God-fearing nation!

04:41.949 --> 04:43.492
Our nation!

04:44.827 --> 04:46.411
Yes!

04:46.412 --> 04:48.121
Yes!

04:48.122 --> 04:51.457
Despite what that little bitch Starlight
tried to do

04:51.458 --> 04:53.292
- at our southern border...
-  Got it!

04:53.293 --> 04:56.212
...is there no depth
to what that little who--

04:56.213 --> 04:58.214
Homelander and Queen Maeve...

04:58.215 --> 05:00.049
my God, they're leaving us.

05:00.050 --> 05:01.676
-  Take these two!
-  Whoa, no.

05:01.677 --> 05:02.969
-  Just these two! Please!
-  No!

05:02.970 --> 05:06.097
What? So they can tell the world that
we left the rest of them to fucking die?

05:06.098 --> 05:07.974
Come on!

05:07.975 --> 05:10.309
No, Maeve.
No. You stay back.

05:10.310 --> 05:12.020
All of you, stay back!

05:12.021 --> 05:13.187
You stay the fuck back

05:13.188 --> 05:14.856
or I'll laser you, goddamn it!

05:14.857 --> 05:16.984
I'll laser every fucking one of you!

05:46.472 --> 05:50.683
This was an AI-generated
disinformation campaign, period.

05:50.684 --> 05:55.104
And the American people have the good
sense to call out a lie when they see--

05:55.105 --> 05:56.981
 Stay back! Or I'll laser

05:56.982 --> 05:58.984
-every fucking one of you!

06:00.611 --> 06:03.154
 ♪ Stay back ♪

06:03.155 --> 06:04.614
♪ I'll laser every fu-- ♪

06:04.615 --> 06:06.240
Ladies and gentlemen,

06:06.241 --> 06:08.327
the vice president of the United States.

06:15.000 --> 06:16.251
Tough day.

06:17.377 --> 06:19.128
Sad day.

06:19.129 --> 06:23.049
When a great American like Homelander
is attacked with lies.

06:23.050 --> 06:26.260
This so-called Flight 37 video
is an obvious deepfake

06:26.261 --> 06:28.137
put out by Marxist Starlighters.

06:28.138 --> 06:30.848
Let's open it up.

06:30.849 --> 06:32.058
Chris Hayes.

06:32.059 --> 06:33.226
Vice President Barrett--

06:33.227 --> 06:34.393
Look, Chris,

06:34.394 --> 06:36.104
I know exactly what you're thinking.
Literally.

06:36.105 --> 06:39.398
And, no, just because I happen to be
a super-abled American

06:39.399 --> 06:42.568
does not compromise my objectivity
or allegiance to the U.S. of A.

06:42.569 --> 06:45.321
That is exactly the kind
of Super-phobic question

06:45.322 --> 06:47.031
that kept me in the closet for so long.

06:47.032 --> 06:48.574
Honestly,

06:48.575 --> 06:49.659
do better?

06:49.660 --> 06:51.536
What about your so-called Freedom Camps

06:51.537 --> 06:52.995
for the Starlighter dissidents?

06:52.996 --> 06:54.288
More clickbait.

06:54.289 --> 06:55.915
I mean, who doesn't love freedom?

06:55.916 --> 06:57.208
- And camp?
-  We knew

06:57.209 --> 06:58.918
this would happen sooner or later.

06:58.919 --> 07:00.128
We've been ready.

07:00.129 --> 07:01.796
In the last 24 hours,

07:01.797 --> 07:04.757
we have flooded the zone
with so much disinformation,

07:04.758 --> 07:06.717
people can't tell their clit
from their collarbone.

07:06.718 --> 07:09.470
The share price is only down half a point.

07:09.471 --> 07:11.597
Besides that, damage is minimal.

07:11.598 --> 07:12.849
What's this?

07:12.850 --> 07:14.016
That is a Gutenberg Bible.

07:14.017 --> 07:16.894
Martin Shkreli sold it to me at discount.

07:16.895 --> 07:19.397
You're really on top of the world, huh?

07:19.398 --> 07:20.481
Peter Thiel,

07:20.482 --> 07:24.069
the Obamas calling you for advice.

07:25.070 --> 07:26.863
Everyone loves you.

07:26.864 --> 07:28.406
You can't really think I care.

07:28.407 --> 07:30.116
Maybe you didn't used to.

07:30.117 --> 07:31.534
It's all for you.

07:31.535 --> 07:33.953
Higher the share price,
happier the billionaires,

07:33.954 --> 07:36.873
the more you get to do
whatever the fuck you want to do.

07:36.874 --> 07:40.376
Are you aware that NNC
is calling me a murderer?

07:40.377 --> 07:42.379
Saying that maybe...

07:43.463 --> 07:46.049
...I even did something to, uh...

07:47.426 --> 07:49.051
...my son.

07:49.052 --> 07:50.553
No. Everyone knows that Ryan is--

07:53.265 --> 07:56.017
Sorry. That he is at boarding school.

07:56.018 --> 07:57.935
In Svalbard.

07:57.936 --> 07:59.312
That story's holding.

07:59.313 --> 08:01.355
-  We're good.
- Mm.

08:01.356 --> 08:03.774
And how-how about you, Sage?

08:03.775 --> 08:05.152
Are you...

08:06.737 --> 08:08.654
- ...good?
- I'm fine.

08:08.655 --> 08:09.906
You're not distracted at all?

08:09.907 --> 08:11.741
After Thomas Godolkin dumped you.

08:11.742 --> 08:14.202
You're not numbing the heartache

08:14.203 --> 08:15.786
by stabbing your brain?

08:15.787 --> 08:18.414
- No.
- Then just tell me.

08:18.415 --> 08:20.459
How did Starlight get in the building?

08:23.545 --> 08:26.340
I was humiliated!

08:27.841 --> 08:29.759
As if people don't hate me enough!

08:29.760 --> 08:31.552
Your numbers are north of 96.

08:31.553 --> 08:33.638
Anyone can smile for the pollsters, sure,

08:33.639 --> 08:36.933
but millions of them
are still Starlighters in their hearts.

08:36.934 --> 08:38.142
Where it counts.

08:38.143 --> 08:40.186
Have you seen the memes?

08:40.187 --> 08:42.522
Have you seen the memes about me?

08:44.816 --> 08:46.734
Posting them...

08:46.735 --> 08:48.069
should be a crime.

08:48.070 --> 08:50.530
Yes. But we can't go...

08:51.823 --> 08:53.908
Oh, you're serious.

08:53.909 --> 08:55.910
Uh, sir.

08:55.911 --> 08:58.371
Ongoing conflict is useful to us.

08:58.372 --> 08:59.622
- It keeps people afraid.
- Shut up.

08:59.623 --> 09:01.416
- Which is exactly what we--
- No, no, no, no, no, no!

09:02.668 --> 09:04.585
You promised me Caesar.

09:04.586 --> 09:06.337
He was stabbed by his best friends.

09:06.338 --> 09:07.713
Yeah, well, I can relate to that.

09:07.714 --> 09:11.759
But I need people to be devoted.

09:11.760 --> 09:13.177
To me.

09:13.178 --> 09:14.595
May I speak freely?

09:14.596 --> 09:15.763
Give it a shot.

09:15.764 --> 09:19.517
I told you, no matter
how much power you amass,

09:19.518 --> 09:20.769
it will not make you happy.

09:27.276 --> 09:29.528
You know what's gonna make me happy?

09:31.071 --> 09:33.823
I think I'll be happy when Starlight

09:33.824 --> 09:36.827
and William Butcher are corpses.

09:40.372 --> 09:42.331
I want it leaked

09:42.332 --> 09:43.499
that, in three days,

09:43.500 --> 09:46.711
we are going to execute
Hugh Campbell, Milk,

09:46.712 --> 09:48.087
and the...

09:48.088 --> 09:49.548
F-French one.

09:50.549 --> 09:53.217
That'll draw out Starlight and Butcher.

09:53.218 --> 09:55.803
And then I will take care of this

09:55.804 --> 09:56.972
once and for all.

09:58.056 --> 09:59.890
Consider it done, sir.

11:12.506 --> 11:14.423
You mind being more careful?

11:14.424 --> 11:15.884
Désolé.

11:17.135 --> 11:19.012
Merci à toi, petit Hughie.

11:20.222 --> 11:21.305
Thank you.

11:21.306 --> 11:22.848
Also,

11:22.849 --> 11:25.601
tales of Annie's exploits.

11:25.602 --> 11:26.937
Enjoy.

11:48.458 --> 11:50.210
Put it on my friend.

12:13.150 --> 12:14.400
Luis.

12:14.401 --> 12:15.986
La bebida.

12:29.958 --> 12:32.543
Annie got
the Flight 37 video out.

12:32.544 --> 12:34.212
Huh.

12:35.547 --> 12:36.964
"Huh"?

12:36.965 --> 12:38.591
That's all you have to say?

12:48.810 --> 12:50.311
No!

13:20.634 --> 13:22.219
Hello, Dad.

13:24.638 --> 13:25.722
Billy.

13:33.396 --> 13:34.813
You are a wanted man.

13:34.814 --> 13:36.774
What are you doing here?

13:36.775 --> 13:38.485
On a bit of a layover.

13:39.903 --> 13:42.071
Thought I'd pop in,

13:42.072 --> 13:44.199
say hello to Lenny and Mum.

13:46.493 --> 13:49.078
Proof there's no God, innit?

13:49.079 --> 13:50.496
She's dead,

13:50.497 --> 13:52.748
and, here you are,

13:52.749 --> 13:55.085
thriving with ass cancer.

14:02.634 --> 14:04.134
Mm.

14:04.135 --> 14:05.886
Does it hurt when you take a shit?

14:05.887 --> 14:07.012
Fucking hope so.

14:07.013 --> 14:10.641
I didn't know how to get hold of you
about the funeral.

14:10.642 --> 14:13.435
I noticed an empty spot next to them
at the churchyard.

14:13.436 --> 14:15.145
You don't think
that's where you're going, do you?

14:15.146 --> 14:16.230
I paid for it.

14:16.231 --> 14:17.690
People like you and me

14:17.691 --> 14:20.318
don't get to spend eternity
with the likes of them.

14:21.987 --> 14:23.320
That what you come here for?

14:23.321 --> 14:25.031
Torture an old man, eh?

14:28.535 --> 14:29.702
Where did you find that?

14:29.703 --> 14:30.953
In the attic.

14:30.954 --> 14:33.081
Reminded me of him.

14:40.964 --> 14:44.092
Five fucking weeks
Lenny practiced that rings trick.

14:45.176 --> 14:47.679
I still remember
the look on his face when he won.

14:48.763 --> 14:50.765
So fucking chuffed.

14:52.976 --> 14:54.728
And then he come home.

14:56.438 --> 14:58.189
And you called him a little poof.

14:59.941 --> 15:01.692
Well...

15:01.693 --> 15:04.320
never looked at this again, did he?

15:04.321 --> 15:05.863
Why are you here?

15:05.864 --> 15:06.990
Huh?

15:16.499 --> 15:18.751
There's no need to get angry.

15:18.752 --> 15:20.128
Oh, I ain't angry.

15:21.129 --> 15:22.755
I'm bleeding grateful.

15:22.756 --> 15:24.840
All the times you knocked
the shit out of me,

15:24.841 --> 15:26.509
gave me the belt or whatever...

15:27.594 --> 15:29.054
...made me who I am.

15:30.388 --> 15:32.514
Made me just like you.

15:32.515 --> 15:34.309
I'll show you.

15:35.393 --> 15:37.936
Son, please.

15:37.937 --> 15:39.230
I know.

15:40.315 --> 15:41.815
I ain't got long to go.

15:41.816 --> 15:44.193
Be a waste-waste of time.

15:44.194 --> 15:45.695
- Mm.
- I know.

15:47.113 --> 15:50.491
But it'll give me a good fucking laugh

15:50.492 --> 15:52.409
just to hear you scream.

15:52.410 --> 15:54.036
It...

15:54.037 --> 15:56.081
it ain't gonna change nothing.

16:03.421 --> 16:05.589
Who says...

16:05.590 --> 16:07.759
I want to change?

16:17.560 --> 16:18.936
What's the matter with you?

16:18.937 --> 16:20.521
- What?
- Your heart's pounding.

16:23.066 --> 16:24.233
Are you scared?

16:24.234 --> 16:26.694
No. I-I just love being at work.

16:26.695 --> 16:28.946
- It's, um... it's exciting.
- Room temperature, like you like.

16:33.410 --> 16:34.869
Have a good show.

16:41.543 --> 16:43.001
I want an 8:00 at Jean-Georges.

16:43.002 --> 16:44.169
Tell 'em it's for me.

16:44.170 --> 16:46.422
Move that Elon interview to Thursday.

16:46.423 --> 16:48.465
And tell Jerry I said, "Fuck off."

16:48.466 --> 16:50.342
If he wants to trim the budget,
how about going after a show

16:50.343 --> 16:52.220
that isn't his biggest fucking hit?

16:58.935 --> 17:00.353
Howdy there, boss.

17:01.688 --> 17:03.440
Don't you look dashing today.

17:04.441 --> 17:06.316
My whole life

17:06.317 --> 17:08.986
has been dedicated to saving these people.

17:08.987 --> 17:13.323
And yet their hearts
are fluttering like...

17:13.324 --> 17:14.700
fucking rabbits.

17:14.701 --> 17:16.452
Wh-Why?

17:16.453 --> 17:17.786
What are they hiding?

17:17.787 --> 17:19.873
Oh, they ain't hiding nothing.

17:20.874 --> 17:23.626
They just look up to you, is all.

17:31.342 --> 17:34.344
Meanwhile, your heart's wheezing away
like it's made of ham and cigarettes.

17:34.345 --> 17:36.263
Sir, I'm so, so sorry.

17:36.264 --> 17:39.726
I want to be making milk, I do,
more than anything, but...

17:40.727 --> 17:43.645
...them pills just janked up my ticker
something awful.

17:45.356 --> 17:47.192
They were killing me.

17:57.160 --> 17:59.369
How'd you catch 'em red-handed?

17:59.370 --> 18:02.873
Our enemies have started using
bleeding-edge technologies.

18:02.874 --> 18:05.876
- Mm.
- Like "AI."

18:05.877 --> 18:08.670
Which means "artificial intelligence."

18:08.671 --> 18:11.673
So Starlight did use that dang-fangled AI.

18:11.674 --> 18:13.425
First she went and deepfaked

18:13.426 --> 18:15.469
Thomas Godolkin himself.

18:15.470 --> 18:17.554
Yeah, but did anyone
actually believe that?

18:17.555 --> 18:20.224
I mean, how stupid
does she think we all are?

18:20.225 --> 18:22.559
To cover up her slaughter

18:22.560 --> 18:24.853
of innocent young heroes at God U.

18:24.854 --> 18:28.607
Then she went and AI'd this so-called

18:28.608 --> 18:30.901
Flight 37 video.

18:30.902 --> 18:32.319
Oh, that's sloppy work.

18:32.320 --> 18:34.071
If we freeze it.

18:34.072 --> 18:35.197
Here. Yeah.

18:36.825 --> 18:39.159
I mean, last I checked,
I do not have seven fingers

18:39.160 --> 18:40.494
- on one hand.
- Now,

18:40.495 --> 18:43.748
isn't that what they refer to
as the uncanny valley?

18:45.124 --> 18:46.333
Yes, it is.

18:54.425 --> 18:56.469
Those smell amazing.

18:57.595 --> 19:01.516
Someone I love very much
taught me how to make them.

19:08.690 --> 19:11.651
Take these to your Mom, OK?

19:45.768 --> 19:46.769
Oi.

19:49.814 --> 19:51.732
Knock it off.

19:51.733 --> 19:54.151
I ain't here for you, you dozy bint.

19:54.152 --> 19:56.028
They're after Frenchie.

19:56.029 --> 19:58.488
Vought's gonna do him,

19:58.489 --> 20:00.366
Hughie, and M in 72 hours.

20:04.370 --> 20:06.288
Look,

20:06.289 --> 20:07.999
I know you don't trust me.

20:09.000 --> 20:10.584
But Frenchie's a dead man.

20:10.585 --> 20:12.002
We ain't got time to fuck about.

20:12.003 --> 20:13.837
I got a CIA Gulfstream

20:13.838 --> 20:15.465
gassing up at Plaridel.

20:16.466 --> 20:17.550
Wheels up in an hour.

20:25.308 --> 20:27.392
Smile, campers.

20:27.393 --> 20:29.603
It's a new day and a new chance

